title: Aikido Yoshinkan -The Complete Set of Techniques (BOXSET DVDrip)
description:
Originally released as a 10 part VHS series titled \"Yoshinkan Complete Set of Techniques\", now this incredible collection is available in a 3 DVD box set. This is regarded as the most complete collection of Aikido techniques on any video set. Techniques are demonstrated by Soke Gozo Shioda and instruction is performed and explained by top Yoshinkan instructors: Tsutomu Chida, Hitoshi Nakano, and Tsuneo Ando. Full English narration by Robert Mustard. 

Contents Include:

Disc 1 (Contains what was previously released on VHS # 1, 2, and 3)

    * Kihon Dosa (Basics) 
	-Rei (Etiquette) 
	-Kamae (Stance) 
	-Shikko Ho (Knee Walking) 
	-The 6 Basic Movements of Yoshinkan Aikido 
	-Ukemi (Falling)
    * Shihonage (14 techniques)
    * Ikkajo (36 techniques)

Disc 2 (Contains what was previously released on VHS # 4, 5, and 6)

    * Nikajo (35 techniques)
    * Sankajo (32 techniques)
    * Yonkajo (28 techniques)

Disc 3 (Contains what was previously released on VHS # 7, 8, 9, and 10)

    * Iriminage (52 techniques)
    * Hijishime and Hiji Ate Kokyu Nage (49 techniques)
    * Kotegaeshi (27 techniques)
    * Tenchinage (4 techniques)
    * Kokyuho (5 techniques)
    * Jiyuwaza (12 techniques)

This series is an indespesible resource for the serious student of Yoshinkan Aikido!

*YOU WILL NOT LEARN THESE TECHNIQUES BY WATCHING ALONE - YOU MUST FIND A QUALIFIED TEACHER, AND TRAIN AS HARD AND AS OFTEN AS YOU CAN FOR AS LONG AS YOU CAN!* 

OSU!
